Beerbaum, Ger) clear 50.76 secs. British: 12 -- Midnight Madness (M
Whitaker) 4 faults 2nd rd, 19 -- Dollar Girl (N Skelton) 4 faults 1st
rd, 30 -- It's Otto (G Billington) 4 faults 1st rd.
