<ARTICLETYPE>OBITUARY</ARTICLETYPE>
<RECORDNO>977584305</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
LOS ANGELES: Gale Gordon, who became a favourite with viewers in three
Lucille Ball television series, has died aged 89. He was suffering from
cancer and died at a nursing home in Los Angeles. His actress wife
Virginia died a few weeks earlier in the same home.
